comments: There were only four shapes so that part was relatively easy with some simple mnemonics. Zetykoh as the explosion - Z is the last letter and an explosion is the last thing you see (bit grim, but it works). Wopykoh as the o in it to represent the circle. I didn't take notes as it became easy after a while. The end task where colours played a factor was harder as there was no way to communicate the colour to the other person. I did enjoy the task however!
